{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982365888,"sessionID":"ses_1cc636d7cffexWEymB04dMSTbm","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_q64RpXUmskXesd2zYvKrXLy2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"https://enzyme.expasy.org/EC/1.13.11.37\\r\\nEntry: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nAccepted Name: hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase\\r\\nReaction catalysed: benzene-1,2,4-triol + O2 <=> 2 H(+) + maleylacetate\\r\\n\\r\\nThat EC is currently on two GO terms (shown below), it's an exact match for the second one (GO:0047074) that describes the 'complete 2-step reaction', but should only be a 'broadMatch' for the first one (GO:0018581) that only describes the first step of the reaction. (The second step in non-enzymatic conversion of 3-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate to maleylacetate - see https://biocyc.org/META/NEW-IMAGE?type=REACTION&object=RXN-10137)\\r\\nTasks:\\r\\n- [x] Make EC:1.13.11.37 xref on GO:0018581 a 'broadMatch'\\r\\n- [x] Remove EC:1.13.11.37-attributed synonyms from GO:0018581 (EC:1.13.11.37 currently doesn't list any synonyms)\\r\\n- [x] Change GO:0018581 def attribution to use RHEA:19441\\r\\n- [x] Make EC:1.13.11.37 xref on GO:0047074 a 'exactMatch'\\r\\n- [x] Tweak GO:0047074 def to match EC:1.13.11.37 def\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nid: GO:0018581\\r\\nname: hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\r\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: benzene-1,2,4-triol + O2 = 3-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate.\\\" [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nsynonym: \\\"benzene-1,2,4-triol:oxygen 1,2-oxidoreductase (decyclizing)\\\" RELATED [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nsynonym: \\\"hydroxyquinol dioxygenase activity\\\" RELATED [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nxref: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:HYDROXYQUINOL-12-DIOXYGENASE-RXN\\r\\nxref: RHEA:19441\\r\\nxref: UM-BBD_reactionID:r0232\\r\\nis_a: GO:0016702 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen, incorporation of two atoms of oxygen\\r\\n\\r\\nid: GO:0047074\\r\\nname: 4-hydroxycatechol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\r\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\r\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: O2 + benzene-1,2,4-triol = maleylacetate.\\\" [RHEA:35595]\\r\\nxref: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:R308-RXN\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-10137\\r\\nxref: RHEA:35595\\r\\nis_a: GO:0016702 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on single... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws5jRjOX\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"sjm41\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Also:\\r\\n\\r\\n- [x] MetaCyc:HYDROXYQUINOL-12-DIOXYGENASE-RXN is obsolete. Replace with RXN-17556.\\r\\n- [x] MetaCyc:R308-RXN is obsolete. Remove.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2023-08-04T12:40:37Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-1665545111\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAQaW9Q\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"sjm41\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"Looking at this one again, we should:\\n- [x] Obsolete GO:0018581, because it's a sub-reaction of RHEA:35595 (it has 0 GO annotations anyway)\\n- [x] Then rename GO:0047074 to \\\"hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\\" (the name currently on GO:0018581), since that's the EC name.\\n\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-24T09:43:43Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n31:         {\n32:           \"content\": \"THUMBS_UP\",\n33:           \"users\": {\n34:             \"totalCount\": 1\n35:           }\n36:         }\n37:       ],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-4312176373\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n40:     },\n41:     {\n42:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABApxQaA\",\n43:       \"author\": {\n44:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n45:       },\n46:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n47:       \"body\": \"Dear all, \\n\\nThe proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0018581 hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\n\\n* The reason for obsoletion is that this term is equivalent to GO:0047074 4-hydroxycatechol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\n\\nThere are no experimental annotations to this term.\\nThere are no mappings to this term.\\nThis term is not present in any subset.\\nThis term is being replaced by GO:0047074 4-hydroxycatechol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\n\\nAny comments can be  added to the issue: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870.\\n\\nThanks, \",\n48:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T20:20:16Z\",\n49:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n50:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n51:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n52:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n53:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-4338765928\",\n54:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n55:     },\n56:     {\n57:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABApyMNg\",\n58:       \"author\": {\n59:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n60:       },\n61:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n62:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please Obsolete GO:0018581 and then rename GO:0047074 to \\\"hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\\".\",\n63:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T20:22:20Z\",\n64:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n65:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n66:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n67:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n68:         {\n69:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n70:           \"users\": {\n71:             \"totalCount\": 1\n72:           }\n73:         }\n74:       ],\n75:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-4338781238\",\n76:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n77:     },\n78:     {\n79:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABApyZ5w\",\n80:       \"author\": {\n81:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n82:       },\n83:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n84:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25075714761)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n85:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T20:22:51Z\",\n86:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n87:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n88:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n89:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n90:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-4338784743\",\n91:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n92:     }\n93:   ],\n94:   \"title\": \"GO terms with EC:1.13.11.37 xref\",\n95:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870\"\n96: }\n\n(End of file - total 96 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"https://enzyme.expasy.org/EC/1.13.11.37\\r\\nEntry: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nAccepted Name: hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase\\r\\nReaction catalysed: benzene-1,2,4-triol + O2 <=> 2 H(+) + maleylacetate\\r\\n\\r\\nThat EC is currently on two GO terms (shown below), it's an exact match for the second one (GO:0047074) that describes the 'complete 2-step reaction', but should only be a 'broadMatch' for the first one (GO:0018581) that only describes the first step of the reaction. (The second step in non-enzymatic conversion of 3-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate to maleylacetate - see https://biocyc.org/META/NEW-IMAGE?type=REACTION&object=RXN-10137)\\r\\nTasks:\\r\\n- [x] Make EC:1.13.11.37 xref on GO:0018581 a 'broadMatch'\\r\\n- [x] Remove EC:1.13.11.37-attributed synonyms from GO:0018581 (EC:1.13.11.37 currently doesn't list any synonyms)\\r\\n- [x] Change GO:0018581 def attribution to use RHEA:19441\\r\\n- [x] Make EC:1.13.11.37 xref on GO:0047074 a 'exactMatch'\\r\\n- [x] Tweak GO:0047074 def to match EC:1.13.11.37 def\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nid: GO:0018581\\r\\nname: hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\r\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: benzene-1,2,4-triol + O2 = 3-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate.\\\" [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nsynonym: \\\"benzene-1,2,4-triol:oxygen 1,2-oxidoreductase (decyclizing)\\\" RELATED [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nsynonym: \\\"hydroxyquinol dioxygenase activity\\\" RELATED [EC:1.13.11.37]\\r\\nxref: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:HYDROXYQUINOL-12-DIOXYGENASE-RXN\\r\\nxref: RHEA:19441\\r\\nxref: UM-BBD_reactionID:r0232\\r\\nis_a: GO:0016702 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen, incorporation of two atoms of oxygen\\r\\n\\r\\nid: GO:0047074\\r\\nname: 4-hydroxycatechol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\\r\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\r\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: O2 + benzene-1,2,4-triol = maleylacetate.\\\" [RHEA:35595]\\r\\nxref: EC:1.13.11.37\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:R308-RXN\\r\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-10137\\r\\nxref: RHEA:35595\\r\\nis_a: GO:0016702 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on single... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws5jRjOX\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"sjm41\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"Also:\\r\\n\\r\\n- [x] MetaCyc:HYDROXYQUINOL-12-DIOXYGENASE-RXN is obsolete. Replace with RXN-17556.\\r\\n- [x] MetaCyc:R308-RXN is obsolete. Remove.\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2023-08-04T12:40:37Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/25870#issuecomment-1665545111\",\n      \"viewe